。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SCDM/111%2c%e6%98%93%2c1%2c20220127%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SCDM,111,易,1,20220127,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"易","JNO":"1","JDATE":"20220127","JTITLE":"詐欺"}